    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>\n                  The limit of detection (LOD) of thirty-two antigen lateral flow tests (Ag-RDT) were evaluated with the SARS-CoV-2 Gamma variant. Twenty-eight of thirty-two Ag-RDTs exceeded the World Health Organization criteria of an LOD of 1.0\u00d710\n                  <jats:sup>6</jats:sup>\n                  genome copy numbers/ml and performance was equivalent as with the 2020 B.1 lineage and Alpha variant.\n                </jats:p>",
